  - greece
Emblem: session/portraits/emblems/emblem_spartans.png
History: The Spartans have some of the strongest infantry in the game, with
  Perioikoi hoplites and Spartiate champions, who both utilize the strong
  phalanx formation. They also receive a free Stoa building, which grants +20%
  health for all buildings, and the Greek Theater, which increases territory
  influence for their buildings. Lastly, they receive 1 free Spartiate champion
  at the start of a standard match.
