TeamBonuses:
  - Name: Peloponnesian League
    History: Much of the Peloponnese was subject to Sparta in one way or another.
      This loose confederation, with Sparta as its leader, was later dubbed the
      Peloponnesian League by historians, but in ancient times was called 'The
      Lacedaemonians and their allies.'
    Description: Allied citizen-soldier spear infantry +10% health.
